WPPConnect API REST (1.1.0)

Download OpenAPI specification:Download

Auth

generate-token (Gera token Bearer para sessão)

Authorizations:
httpBearer
path Parameters
secretkey
required
string
Example: THISISMYSECURETOKEN

(Required) chave do admin

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/{secretkey}/generate-token

Response samples

  • 201
Content type
application/json
{
  • "status": "Success",
  • "session": "nova",
  • "token": "$2b$10$N9xrdqCW4S1jpNyB44L1nuXj79EAvo83MS6uxhBg8JOvWNLV8QlaS",
  • "full": "nova:$2b$10$N9xrdqCW4S1jpNyB44L1nuXj79EAvo83MS6uxhBg8JOvWNLV8QlaS"
}

start-session (Retorna QRCode de login)

Inicializa a sessão

Authorizations:
httpBearer
Request Body schema: application/json
webhook
required
string

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/start-session

Request samples

  • Payload
Content type
application/json
{
  • "webhook": "https://webhook.site/7cc2944d-3967-4cea-988c-d57ea80bce5f"
}

status-session (Atualiza QRCode de login)

Retorna o status da session

Authorizations:
httpBearer

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/status-session

qrcode-session (Pegar qrCode de autenticação via stream)

Retorna o status da session

Authorizations:
httpBearer

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/qrcode-session

check-connection-session (status da conexão)

Verifica se a sessáo esta conectada

Authorizations:
httpBearer

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/check-connection-session

close-session

finaliza a sessão

Authorizations:
httpBearer

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/close-session

Get messages in Chat

Get messages in chat.

Authorizations:
httpBearer
path Parameters
phone
required
string

The contact ID, with @c.us or @g.us

query Parameters
count
integer
Example:

Quantity of messages. Specify -1 to get everything (may take a long time).

id
string
Example:

Get messages after/before this message ID.

direction
string
Example:

Specify the direction in which the messages are gonna be retrieved. If present, must be 'after' or 'before'

header Parameters
Content-Type
required
string
Example: application/json
